  "title": "Admin Assistant (Sales Support)",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Manufacturing industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>Admin Assistant (Sales Support) </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Permanent</li>\n  <li><strong>Position:</strong> Admin Assistant (Sales Support)</li>\n  <li><strong>Location:</strong> West</li>\n  <li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, 8.30am to 5.30pm</li>\n  <li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Up to $3,500 + AWS + Bonus</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage customer inquiries through various communication channels and provide information on product availability, delivery schedules, and shipment details.</li>\n  <li>Process and verify sales orders accurately and promptly in the system.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with supply chain, logistics, and warehouse teams to ensure timely delivery.</li>\n  <li>Handle shipping and customs documentation, liaising with forwarders and shipping agents.</li>\n  <li>Prepare sales reports, track order records, and support sales meetings.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with internal departments to resolve queries and discrepancies.</li>\n  <li>Verify and reconcile purchase orders, invoices, and delivery notes.</li>\n  <li>Negotiate freight rates with appointed forwarders to ensure cost efficiency.</li>\n  <li>Prioritize and manage multiple tasks to meet deadlines effectively.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least GCE “O” Level and minimum 2 years of experience in handling sales order processing.</li>\n  <li>Familiar with Microsoft Office.</li>\n  <li>Able to start immediately or in short notice.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Click the APPLY button, or</li>\n  <li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p>\n<p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
